<subSubSection pageId="58" pageNumber="453" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="58.[1395,2602,733,1200]" pageId="58" pageNumber="453">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1398,1745,1049,1082]" pageId="58" pageNumber="453">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Lesser Taiwanese Brown-toothed Shrew is the least known shrew in Taiwan, known only from a dozen specimens.
</paragraph>
